     Chemical-Formula is used to represent both molecular-formulae and empirical-formulae, 
     since there is no sctutural difference between them. Note that a molecular formula 
     is the filler of the <slot>moelcular-formula</slot> slot; similar for empirical formula.
  </comment>

</examplesentencelist>

